38
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,180
=Guardians of the Dafeng=

39
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:44,140
=Episode 33=

40
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,910
So is that man in black

41
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,960
coveting my fortune?

42
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:53,190
Here's a friendly reminder.

43
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,910
Before Shen Shu reemerges,

44
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:57,110
do not set foot outside the Dafeng.

45
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,520
Let me tell you.

46
00:02:07,990 --> 00:02:09,710
Prime Minister Wang

47
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,760
seems like a reasonable person.

48
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,110
- Really.
- Really?

49
00:02:14,110 --> 00:02:15,080
Of course.

50
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,540
What are you doing with the saber?

51
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,200
To practice it.

52
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:33,200
Did we really talk for that long?

53
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:35,110
It's already mealtime.

54
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:38,200
Let's go to eat.

55
00:02:39,830 --> 00:02:42,390
Why do I feel sore in my arm
after talking to you?

56
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:43,880
You have shoulder inflammation.

57
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:46,390
Senior,

58
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,270
are we really leaving like this?

59
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:50,760
The Supervisor is right.

60
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,800
Staying by his side

61
00:02:53,990 --> 00:02:55,760
is the best for Shen Shu.

62
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,320
Father,

63
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:12,000
the wind is strong at night.

64
00:03:12,270 --> 00:03:13,270
Get some rest early.

65
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:15,870
It's getting late.

66
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,360
You should rest now.

67
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:31,580
(Noble Ambitions)

68
00:03:32,990 --> 00:03:34,270
There's something

69
00:03:34,390 --> 00:03:36,430
on Xu Qi'an's body that belongs to me.

70
00:03:36,550 --> 00:03:38,390
You can have Shen Shu,

71
00:03:38,390 --> 00:03:39,520
but I must have

72
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:41,270
Xu Qi'an.

73
00:03:41,990 --> 00:03:43,470
(He's been eyeing me for a long time.)

74
00:03:43,830 --> 00:03:44,960
(When did this start?)

75
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:48,240
(I'm just a small Guardian.)

76
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:49,870
(If he wants to take me away,)

77
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:51,390
(he must have many ways.)

78
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:54,740
(Tax Silver Case Closing File)

79
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:58,540
(Xu Qi'an was sentenced
to exile in Yunzhou.)

80
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,520
(During the Tax Silver Case,)

81
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,590
(I was going to be exiled to Yunzhou.)

82
00:04:04,580 --> 00:04:07,220
(Zhou Li Kidnapping Zhang Yunying)

83
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:09,920
Do you want to be tortured
before signing it

84
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,640
or sign it before being tortured?

85
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,900
(Confession)

86
00:04:15,830 --> 00:04:17,560
(From the Tax Silver Case)

87
00:04:18,470 --> 00:04:20,000
(to Zhou Li's case,)

88
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,120
(were they all to convict me)

89
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,760
(and exile me to Yunzhou?)

90
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:28,660
(Yunzhou)

91
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,280
My Lord,

92
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:52,570
sorry for my incompetence.

93
00:04:53,030 --> 00:04:54,710
I didn't bring Xu Qi'an
out of the Dafeng.

94
00:04:55,230 --> 00:04:56,270
Please punish me.

95
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,110
It's okay.

96
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,350
With the Supervisor protecting him
in the capital,

97
00:04:59,350 --> 00:05:01,880
even the two Prophets
of Tianyu are helpless.

98
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:04,520
Why should you belittle yourself?

99
00:05:04,590 --> 00:05:05,430
My Lord,

100
00:05:06,470 --> 00:05:07,790
what about our plan?

101
00:05:10,230 --> 00:05:11,390
When the time comes,

102
00:05:11,910 --> 00:05:13,440
he will naturally come.

103
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:14,670
Yes.

104
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:19,680
(But I've been to Yunzhou.)

105
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,760
(I even retrieved the tax silver.)

106
00:05:22,150 --> 00:05:24,030
(The man in black didn't take me away.)

107
00:05:24,470 --> 00:05:26,590
(He only placed Shen Shu inside me.)

108
00:05:27,230 --> 00:05:28,440
(Why is that?)

109
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,520
He's formidable.

110
00:05:32,350 --> 00:05:33,710
What we know for sure is that

111
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:35,760
he's a Hypnotizer of The Witcher's Sect.

112
00:05:36,150 --> 00:05:38,120
He told us about Shen Shu

113
00:05:38,230 --> 00:05:40,790
to force us into a conflict
with the Supervisor,

114
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,960
so he could take you out of the Dafeng.

115
00:05:43,710 --> 00:05:44,560
(The Supervisor.)

116
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:47,270
(The man in black fears the Supervisor.)

117
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:50,540
(The only explanation is
that after the Zhou Li Case,)

118
00:05:50,910 --> 00:05:53,590
(the man in black knew
the Supervisor had noticed me.)

119
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:56,590
(He couldn't take me away
under the Supervisor's nose.)

120
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:57,940
(So,)

121
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:59,960
(he placed Shen Shu inside me,)

122
00:06:00,150 --> 00:06:01,320
(using him as a tool.)

123
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,710
(With this,)

124
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,440
(everything makes sense.)

125
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,830
(The man in black wants to take me,)

126
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,370
(while the Supervisor has been
secretly protecting me.)

127
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,200
(They've been plotting in the shadows,)

128
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,760
(like a hidden line in the grass.)

129
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:15,790
(Countless subtle battles
have taken place.)

130
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,200
(And all of this)

131
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:20,080
(is for the strange fortune inside me.)

132
00:06:20,710 --> 00:06:22,000
(And this fortune)

133
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,710
(is the Palace's secret treasure.)

134
00:06:25,470 --> 00:06:26,790
I don't even know

135
00:06:26,910 --> 00:06:29,350
where those little thieves

136
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,000
from 19 years ago went.

137
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,760
Xu Qi'an,

138
00:06:36,590 --> 00:06:37,520
what are you doing

139
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,790
in the Manual Archive so late?

140
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:41,760
Are you on a great mission
from Lord Wei?

141
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,280
No.

142
00:06:48,150 --> 00:06:49,270
Then what's behind you?

143
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:52,110
The Tax Silver Case, right?

144
00:06:53,150 --> 00:06:53,990
Yes.

145
00:06:54,350 --> 00:06:55,830
These cases were closed long ago.

146
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,640
What's the hidden secret?

147
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:01,560
Why has Father also been
reading them these days?

148
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:07,070
Lord Wei

149
00:07:08,660 --> 00:07:10,270
has also been reviewing these old cases?

150
00:07:10,350 --> 00:07:11,350
Not only that,

151
00:07:11,590 --> 00:07:14,520
he also asked me to bring
everything related to these files

152
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,000
from the Municipal Office.

153
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,230
He said someone would review it.

154
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:20,910
I didn't expect it to be you.

155
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,910
Come out.

156
00:08:12,710 --> 00:08:13,850
Do you have something to say?

157
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:14,750
Yes.

158
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,560
Wine.

159
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:24,670
Tell me.

160
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,800
Lord Wei,

161
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,350
when I was back home...

162
00:08:27,350 --> 00:08:28,190
No.

163
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:30,350
When I was in Changle County as a Speed,

164
00:08:30,590 --> 00:08:33,040
I learned a drinking game
from a commoner.

165
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:36,220
It's based on the points of the dice.

166
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,470
The one with the smaller points

167
00:08:37,470 --> 00:08:38,960
either answers a question

168
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,200
or drinks a cup of wine.

169
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:43,200
I'd like to play this game with you.

170
00:08:44,470 --> 00:08:45,960
If you don't want to drink,

171
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,960
then speak your true thoughts.

172
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:53,080
If you're not interested,

173
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,750
I'll leave now.

174
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,030
Do you really want to play?

175
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,630
(Point: 4, 5, 9)

176
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,560
(Point: 9, 9, 9)

177
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:21,750
Then I'll ask first.

178
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,160
Lord Wei,

179
00:09:25,470 --> 00:09:26,310
what is

180
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,920
your relationship with the Empress?

181
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:33,040
You seem to know quite a lot.

182
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,870
I might tell you

183
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,160
about this later,

184
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,280
but right now,

185
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,280
it has nothing to do with your concern.

186
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,320
(Point: 5, 6, 11)

187
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,630
(Point: 9, 9, 9)

188
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,230
Lord Wei, do you remember

189
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,470
what happened in the Palace

190
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:05,230
during the Battle of Linyuan Pass?

191
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,200
If you're asking about the theft

192
00:10:09,350 --> 00:10:11,510
of the Palace's secret treasure,

193
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,510
I know about that.

194
00:10:13,830 --> 00:10:15,700
The thief waited for the right moment

195
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:16,680
and stole the treasure.

196
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,990
By the time we noticed,

197
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:19,000
he had already

198
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:21,320
fled the Dafeng.

199
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:23,350
What was that treasure?

200
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:24,920
I think

201
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,590
it was the national fortune

202
00:10:27,350 --> 00:10:29,680
of the Dafeng that was stolen.

203
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,680
Still want to play?

204
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:44,590
Sure.

205
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:48,920
(Point: 9, 9, 9)

206
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,800
(Point: 9, 9, 9)

207
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,990
How rare.

208
00:10:57,960 --> 00:11:00,080
We can each ask one question.

209
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,920
Alright.

210
00:11:01,230 --> 00:11:02,160
What is

211
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,440
the national fortune?

212
00:11:04,990 --> 00:11:06,560
Among the various systems,

213
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:10,960
the ones most closely related to fortune
are the Bureau and the Academy.

214
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:12,040
The Men Sect

215
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,320
is only half of it.

216
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:15,350
And independent of them,

217
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,960
the foundation of the nation

218
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,230
is represented
by the Dafeng's national fortune.

219
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,620
(Rule With Virtue)

220
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:37,470
Whenever war begins,

221
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:40,020
it marks the start
of the shaking of the national fortune.

222
00:11:41,990 --> 00:11:43,040
Victory

223
00:11:43,110 --> 00:11:44,510
will increase the national fortune.

224
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:45,590
Defeat

225
00:11:46,350 --> 00:11:47,990
will decrease it.

226
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:50,440
The larger the scale of the battle,

227
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:53,560
the more violently
the national fortune shakes.

228
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:56,470
In the Battle of Linyuan Pass
in Yuanjing Year 17,

229
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:57,870
the nations were in chaos,

230
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:01,440
and the total number of troops involved
exceeded a million.

231
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:02,990
The scale was so massive

232
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:06,040
that it's rare in history.

233
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,830
The shaking of the national fortune

234
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,110
was also unprecedented.

235
00:12:12,830 --> 00:12:14,040
The thief,

236
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:16,990
taking advantage of its shaking,

237
00:12:17,230 --> 00:12:18,400
stole the national fortune.

238
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:20,320
For the following 20 years,

239
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,320
the Dafeng

240
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,960
has been on edge

241
00:12:23,230 --> 00:12:25,200
with constant war and natural disasters.

242
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:28,230
His Majesty sent people several times

243
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,590
to investigate,

244
00:12:31,110 --> 00:12:33,590
but the thief's tracks were elusive,

245
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:34,990
and the matter remains unsolved.

246
00:12:39,110 --> 00:12:40,830
What would happen if it's recovered?

247
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,200
We'll have good harvests

248
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:45,960
and a prosperous nation

249
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,590
that is unparalleled

250
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:49,040
in the world.

251
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,710
What if it can't be recovered?

252
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:52,230
Surrounded by wolves and tigers,

253
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:53,750
the Dafeng

254
00:12:54,350 --> 00:12:55,400
will be in danger.

255
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:04,830
Now, it's my turn to ask.

256
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:13,350
The national fortune of the Dafeng

257
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:17,110
is inside you, isn't it?

258
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:22,830
Not only that,

259
00:13:22,990 --> 00:13:24,920
the sealed object under Sangbo Lake

260
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,870
is also within you.

261
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:34,960
In that case,

262
00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:37,110
proceed with Xu Qi'an's matter

263
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,870
as you all said.

264
00:13:41,110 --> 00:13:43,280
Your Majesty, how wise of you.

265
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,200
Continue.

266
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,110
There's no need
to keep rolling the dice.

267
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:53,590
Lord Wei,

268
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,400
when I was in Yunzhou,

269
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,230
the evil object entered my body.

270
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,510
This person is from Tianyu

271
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:02,750
and is named Shen Shu.

272
00:14:03,350 --> 00:14:05,200
But he has no memory of the past

273
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,960
and knows nothing about it.

274
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:08,910
I only discovered

275
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,320
through the remaining fragments

276
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,470
that it was a man in black

277
00:14:11,470 --> 00:14:13,800
who intentionally
placed him inside me...

278
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:16,280
Afterward, you began
investigating his identity,

279
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:17,710
came to ask me

280
00:14:17,830 --> 00:14:19,470
about the Battle of Linyuan Pass,

281
