00:27:12,990 --> 00:27:13,960
Once you reach Chuzhou,

567
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:16,960
don't conflict
with Duke Zhenbei's subordinates.

568
00:27:17,710 --> 00:27:18,990
Present yourself as weak.

569
00:27:19,230 --> 00:27:20,640
This will protect you

570
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:22,920
and make the enemy relax.

571
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:24,600
Once you have the evidence,

572
00:27:24,880 --> 00:27:26,750
quietly bring it back to the capital.

573
00:27:27,470 --> 00:27:28,790
Lord Wei's plans for you

574
00:27:29,510 --> 00:27:32,310
are indeed profound.

575
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,840
He's thought of everything.

576
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:35,920
You came here today

577
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:38,310
on Lord Wei's orders, didn't you?

578
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:40,120
Lord Wei said

579
00:27:40,600 --> 00:27:42,160
you have something

580
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,790
I really need.

581
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:45,360
What is it?

582
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:46,840
Lord Wei didn't say,

583
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:48,230
but he did say

584
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:50,400
you'd definitely help me.

585
00:28:00,820 --> 00:28:03,860
(Second Sage's Hall)

586
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:26,510
This is

587
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:28,470
the image of the Second Sage.

588
00:28:30,710 --> 00:28:33,960
When one dies
for righteousness patriotically,

589
00:28:34,550 --> 00:28:37,030
one's name will always be remembered.

590
00:28:37,790 --> 00:28:39,030
Cheng Hui.

591
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:42,270
Two hundred years ago,

592
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:44,200
Cheng left the Academy

593
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:46,070
and joined the Directorate.

594
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:50,200
He recruited students
from outside the Academy

595
00:28:50,470 --> 00:28:52,030
and set up this inscription.

596
00:28:53,310 --> 00:28:54,750
I'm ashamed to say

597
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,640
that until now,

598
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:58,680
no one has been able to break it.

599
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:09,270
(The Second Sage's Knife.)

600
00:29:21,120 --> 00:29:22,230
When you return safely

601
00:29:22,790 --> 00:29:24,680
from Chuzhou,

602
00:29:25,230 --> 00:29:28,200
return this book to me personally.

603
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,750
Thank you, Mr. Zhao.

604
00:29:33,780 --> 00:29:37,060
(The Lost in the Wilderness)

605
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,200
These books

606
00:29:48,470 --> 00:29:49,880
were all from the Dean?

607
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:52,910
Yes.

608
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:55,200
Why did he give you so many books?

609
00:30:03,790 --> 00:30:05,230
Alright, stop being jealous.

610
00:30:05,230 --> 00:30:06,470
Take a look at this book for me.

611
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:07,400
Have you heard of it?

612
00:30:07,600 --> 00:30:08,840
What's so mysterious about it?

613
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:11,310
The Lost in the Wilderness.

614
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:16,630
I don't know.

615
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:18,470
I don't have the qualifications

616
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:20,640
or the opportunity

617
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:22,980
to enter Second Sage's Hall
and study the books.

618
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,280
But

619
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,120
I've read the history of the Academy,

620
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:33,230
so I know its origin.

621
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:36,460
What's so mysterious about it?

622
00:30:37,470 --> 00:30:39,160
This book was sent by the Bureau

623
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,440
twenty years ago.

624
00:30:41,120 --> 00:30:42,400
Since it was delivered,

625
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:44,030
it's been placed in the Hall

626
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,640
and hasn't been returned.

627
00:30:47,070 --> 00:30:48,400
(The Bureau.)

628
00:30:49,270 --> 00:30:50,790
(The Bureau again.)

629
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:52,270
What's wrong?

630
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:55,590
Nothing.

631
00:30:58,710 --> 00:30:59,960
I still don't understand

632
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:02,600
why the Dean gave you
so many books.

633
00:31:05,710 --> 00:31:07,400
Are you planning
to read all of them here?

634
00:31:07,550 --> 00:31:08,550
Aren't you hungry?

635
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,520
Don't disturb me.

636
00:31:11,030 --> 00:31:11,870
Cijiu.

637
00:31:12,470 --> 00:31:13,310
Shall we go home?

638
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,640
What's this character?

639
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,540
I don't know.

640
00:31:18,550 --> 00:31:19,880
Aren't you a scholar?

641
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:21,070
I don't know.

642
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:32,800
Let's go.

643
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,640
Let's kill a sheep and eat it.

644
00:31:42,180 --> 00:31:44,180
(The Lost in the Wilderness)

645
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:10,060
(Gazing Spell)

646
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:48,420
(The Lost in the Wilderness)

647
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:52,390
Catch it.

648
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:54,640
Pass it to me.

649
00:33:54,840 --> 00:33:56,230
- Give it to me.
- Hurry up.

650
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,240
Hurry up.

651
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:00,550
You serve.

652
00:34:09,240 --> 00:34:10,670
Your Highness, catch it.

653
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,160
Your Highness,

654
00:34:17,190 --> 00:34:18,840
look at the clear sky today.

655
00:34:18,840 --> 00:34:20,800
It's a perfect time to play woven ball.

656
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:23,360
We've played for seven days.

657
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:25,640
Indeed.

658
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,160
Well,

659
00:34:27,720 --> 00:34:29,110
let me push you on the swing.

660
00:34:29,240 --> 00:34:30,720
I can push you very high.

661
00:34:31,240 --> 00:34:33,110
You can't push me out of the Palace.

662
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:34,190
Of course,

663
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:35,990
I can't.

664
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:37,760
Your Highness,

665
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,360
just endure for two more days.

666
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:41,720
When your mother sees
how well-behaved you are,

667
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,590
she will naturally
lift your restrictions.

668
00:34:45,070 --> 00:34:46,240
How annoying.

669
00:34:47,240 --> 00:34:48,630
Where's Xu Qi'an?

670
00:34:48,630 --> 00:34:49,770
Why hasn't he come to see me?

671
00:34:50,720 --> 00:34:52,630
Mr. Xu

672
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,470
might be busy

673
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:55,590
with official matters,

674
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:56,800
or maybe he has

675
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,470
a case to investigate

676
00:34:58,670 --> 00:34:59,720
and is unable to come.

677
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:00,720
Xuan,

678
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:02,150
didn't I tell you to investigate?

679
00:35:02,150 --> 00:35:02,990
What did you find?

680
00:35:04,670 --> 00:35:05,550
Your Highness.

681
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:08,670
Mr. Xu goes to the yamen every day
for roll call.

682
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:11,190
But a few days ago,
he went to Yunlu Academy,

683
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:12,840
and yesterday he went to the Bureau.

684
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,360
Why did he go to those places?

685
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,800
What about today?

686
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:17,760
Today...

687
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:20,360
Today...

688
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,600
He's just

689
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:26,510
listening to music at the brothel.

690
00:35:26,510 --> 00:35:27,350
What?

691
00:35:27,990 --> 00:35:29,320
He has time to go to the brothel

692
00:35:29,320 --> 00:35:30,400
but no time to come see me?

693
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,760
How can this be?

694
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:34,870
Your Highness,

695
00:35:35,110 --> 00:35:36,840
maybe listening to music

696
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:38,990
is part of Mr. Xu's investigation.

697
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:40,670
Let's not overthink it.

698
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:42,360
Let's continue to play.

699
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:54,990
Gang.

700
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:58,240
You've been here since you were five.

701
00:35:59,630 --> 00:36:00,470
It's been

702
00:36:00,630 --> 00:36:02,110
over eleven years now.

703
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:06,070
In these eleven years,

704
00:36:06,990 --> 00:36:08,600
you and I have spent every day together,

705
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:10,360
with one heart and mind.

706
00:36:11,670 --> 00:36:13,510
I know you very well.

707
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:16,840
When you're nervous, you sweat.

708
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:21,320
Maybe

709
00:36:21,590 --> 00:36:22,760
it's because it's too hot.

710
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,670
When you lie, your hands shake.

711
00:36:29,720 --> 00:36:30,590
Tell me the truth.

712
00:36:31,590 --> 00:36:32,800
Where did Xu Qi'an go?

713
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:35,840
You guys hurry up.

714
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:36,920
Sure, Mr. Xu.

715
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:39,940
Hurry and check.

716
00:36:39,950 --> 00:36:41,190
Make sure everything's packed.

717
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,030
Yes.

718
00:36:54,720 --> 00:36:55,920
Remember what I said.

719
00:36:56,240 --> 00:36:58,510
Once we get to Chuzhou, follow the plan.

720
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,550
With your name as the Winged Woman,

721
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:01,760
I'm sure it won't be hard.

722
00:37:02,990 --> 00:37:04,470
Got it.

723
00:37:04,470 --> 00:37:06,150
It was my decision to go,

724
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:08,190
but why does it sound
like you're sending me?

725
00:37:08,990 --> 00:37:10,630
If this trip goes smoothly,

726
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:12,240
you will help me a lot.

727
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:13,360
Consider me owing you one.

728
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,720
How do I contact you in Chuzhou?

729
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,630
Xinnian gave me this.

730
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:27,910
Bye.

731
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:29,550
Mr. Xu, please hurry up.

732
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,670
I'm waiting for you.

733
00:37:32,630 --> 00:37:33,800
Safe travels.

734
00:37:35,110 --> 00:37:36,030
This journey

735
00:37:36,030 --> 00:37:37,320
concerns the greater good,

736
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,440
so you don't owe me.

737
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:40,760
See you in Chuzhou.

738
00:37:42,630 --> 00:37:43,470
By the way,

739
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,440
don't call me Winged Woman.

740
00:37:45,550 --> 00:37:46,550
It's so stupid.

741
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:47,920
Are you going or not?

742
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:49,950
Let's go.

743
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:55,920
Drink less on the way,

744
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:56,840
or you'll ruin things.

745
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,550
You're really noisy.

746
00:38:14,550 --> 00:38:15,800
Everyone, go back.

747
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,320
The boat's about to leave.

748
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:18,800
I have to get on.

749
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:25,620
Aunt,

750
00:38:25,700 --> 00:38:26,990
I won't bring pickled vegetables.

751
00:38:26,990 --> 00:38:28,130
My stomach's been bad lately.

752
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,460
I won't be able to eat them.

753
00:38:32,190 --> 00:38:33,110
Uncle,

754
00:38:33,190 --> 00:38:34,110
I have my own saber.

755
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:36,030
The boat is also equipped with armor.

756
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,990
Put it away. It's dangerous.

757
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:43,720
Sis,

758
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:44,680
what's this?

759
00:38:46,540 --> 00:38:47,820
(Qi'an)

760
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:49,360
An amulet.

761
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,200
Alright.

762
00:38:51,470 --> 00:38:52,400
I'll take it.

763
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:55,310
By the way,

764
00:38:55,310 --> 00:38:57,360
I'll buy you Butter Jade from Chuzhou.

765
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:58,200
It's their specialty.

766
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,760
Little one,

767
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:03,840
I'm leaving.

768
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:05,030
Will you miss me?

769
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:07,990
Ningyan, when will you come back?

770
00:39:08,110 --> 00:39:10,720
I'll come back
when you memorize the Disciple Rules.

771
00:39:11,360 --> 00:39:13,400
Ningyan won't be coming back.

772
00:39:15,190 --> 00:39:16,600
Stop talking nonsense. Take it back.

773
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,280
Ningyan,

774
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:20,840
be careful.

775
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:23,190
Don't repeat the last time.

776
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:25,110
Last time your aunt

777
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:28,360
didn't eat or drink, cried nonstop,

778
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:29,960
and almost passed out.

779
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:32,280
Who passed out?

780
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:34,030
That didn't happen. Impossible.

781
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:37,800
It's a long journey.

782
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,510
You must be careful.

783
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:44,840
Write to tell us you're safe
when you get there. Got it?

784
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:47,800
Don't worry, Aunt.

785
00:39:58,240 --> 00:39:59,320
And you.

786
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:01,630
I won't waste words on you.

787
00:40:01,630 --> 00:40:02,800
Enjoy your life with Simu.

788
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:04,880
Hurry. I'm waiting for the wedding wine.

789
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,200
Ningyan,

790
00:40:06,470 --> 00:40:07,360
that's inappropriate.

791
00:40:07,470 --> 00:40:08,760
How can you just...

792
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:11,460
Thank you for your kind words, Ningyan.

793
00:40:11,760 --> 00:40:12,800
I wish you

794
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:13,670
a smooth journey.

795
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:14,920
May this trip not be in vain.

796
00:40:14,990 --> 00:40:16,310
We'll be waiting
for your return.

797
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:17,440
Look at her.

798
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:18,670
You're a grown man,

799
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:20,150
but you aren't as good as a girl.

800
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:21,070
Exactly.

801
00:40:21,070 --> 00:40:22,280
How can you say that about me?

802
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:24,550
Princess Lin'an is still grounded
in the Palace.

803
00:40:25,150 --> 00:40:26,110
Before you go,

804
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:27,990
did you say goodbye to her?

805
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,440
You talk too much.

806
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:39,390
Alright.

807
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,600
I'm leaving now.

